data.description: Fabulous Find on lovely LAKE VIEW Home in desirable Soda Bay area of Kelseyville. Recent rehab, remodel and appraisal has the "effective age" at 5 years. Walk to the community pier and Bell Haven Gardens. There's a large covered lake view deck, new privacy fencing and storage shed in side yard with deck. Oversized lot has ample parking for RV and boat storage with power and water hook up.  High Efficiency split system HVAC units offer cost effective heating and cooling. Recent pest, home and septic inspections are on file.  This home is squeaky clean and ready for summer fun on beautiful Clear Lake
